title: 05/18/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 05/18/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP previews tonight's Play-in tournament games. Will there be more of the play-in tournament in years to come? The MMQB's Albert Breer discusses the latest on the Aaron Rodger's situation. Has anyone confirmed that Aaron actually wants out of Green Bay? And Chris Mannix explains why people are gravitating toward Youtubers boxing.
